\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 ## What Largent Does
\f1\b0 \cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 Largent is built to help users:\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
