\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 Largent provides estimation tools, budgeting workflows, and organizational reporting. Any tax, paycheck, deduction, or budget calculation presented in the product is an estimate for planning purposes only and should not be treated as official tax, payroll, accounting, or legal advice.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Users are responsible for confirming their actual tax obligations, withholding setup, payroll deductions, and financial decisions with appropriate professionals or institutions.\cb1 \
